imdb.plot outline: "Guy in Dubai" is an on-demand TV series that is guide to the fun, extreme and exciting side of Dubai. On a mission to hunt the thrills that only the City of Dubai can offer, this entertaining series shows residents and tourists how they can take part in such fun and inspires the audience to step outside of their comfort zone and live it today. Season 1 was a hit on OSN's on-demand where 22 episodes have been launched. Guy in Dubai is also licensed across the UAE to Hotels for their room TV's.
